<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Abstract By permeating historical trajectories, this text seeks to discuss the relations between architectural thought and the contemporary city, and how the political, economic, social and cultural contexts must be considered in any process that deals with the complexity of the urban condition that surrounds us.]]></p></abstract>
